parameters: \n<Abigail>\}P-\.please,\. d-\.don't tell Lady Anzu what happened...\.\.\. I'd lose my job...\{
"My research has been driving me to find some rather questionable things.\.\. No,\. questionable is a wrong term.\.\. Infuriating is more correct."

"The company has been exposing normal people from the Surface Stratum to Mana.\.\. Completely innocent,\. UNWILLING civilians,\. dragged out from their homes in the shadows to be brought down to the Hole to be experimented on..."
"Many of the "official" sources claim nothing illegal was ever happening,\. but if the company's influence spreads as far as it seems like it does..."
"...then it's not out of the question that they're manipulating the public eye when and how it suits them."
\n<Abigail>\}...\.\.\. w-\.elcome...\.\.\. s-\.so sorry about what happened.\{
\n<???>!!\.\. A c-\.c-\.customer!?\.\. I'm A-\.Abigail,\. welcome to m-\.my lady's library!
\n<Abigail>I-\.if you want t-\.to burrow a book,\. I'll be here!
"Subject 13,\. died shortly after being exposed to mana after suffering a severe heart attack.\.\. Body disposed of and made to look like an accident."
"Subject 60,\. began showing symptoms of mental instability as early as three days after exposure.\.\. Rendered totally insane after two weeks of exposure."

"Subject 178,\. further understanding of mana exposure had delayed the symptoms of mental instability,\. but after insanity had occurred,\. the subject was found dead and frothing at the mouth in their detention ward three days later."

"Subject 258,\. looked to be fine for the most part until going to sleep and never waking up again after about a month of exposure.\.\. As far as the records go,\. was kept in a medicated coma for future evaluation."

"Subject 339,\. by far the most mentally unstable of most subjects we've had so far.\.\. Despite extensive security measures put in place to ensure nothing goes wrong,\. the subject had managed to break free of restraints,\. attack researchers and escape the facility.\.\. Disappeared down the Hole,\. effectively considered dead."

"Amidst my research,\. I began to look for the possible cause of my ever-growing insomnia problem.\.\. Apparently some divers who went into the hole have encountered certain monsters which could induce similar symptoms."

"This effect seems to be caused by their bodies surviving continuous exposure to high levels of mana.\.\. After their body accumulates enough resistance,\. it can actually form a bizarre symbiotic relationship with the microorganisms that were once harmful to it."
"After a while longer,\. those microorganisms are so prevalent within the beasts that they start to radiate the mana,\. causing possible harm to divers who spend too much time fighting them."

"These monsters seem to exist in areas within the second strata,\. but are more commonly found in areas even lower than that.\.\. Their occurrence becomes more and more frequent the deeper one goes into the hole,\. where mana exposure becomes more and more dangerous."
"No monster like this has ever been allowed to reach the surface stratum,\. and information is kept fairly well guarded.\.\. No wonder nobody knows about this."

"Was Lady Anzu exposed to this level of Mana in the Hole?\.\. That wouldn't make sense...\.\.\. none of the other maids are developing similar symptoms.\.\. Though their symptoms might be different than mine.\.\. Miss Kanako would kill me if she found out I'm even considering such a thing,\. but how else could this have happened?"
"I managed to find some public records about an experiment the company had conducted regarding the effects of relics on normal people..."

"Strangely enough,\. the data doesn't look outright modified or made up,\. but it was likely skewed by the researchers,\. or presented in such a way where the true results aren't immediately obvious.\.\. After all,\. this experiment was conducted exclusively by company contractors,\. there's no way it can be trusted completely."

"I've got a feeling that's what that little part at the end of the report was about.\.\. "Exposure to extended periods of time is not recommended,\. and particularly sensitive individuals should be kept away from relics.\.\." That's where the truth lies...\.\.\. in that little disclosure there!\.\. I know it!\.\. It has to be!"
"I'm talking like some crazy conspiracy theorist...\.\.\. but am I wrong to be worried about what these people are doing?!"
"I can barely think straight these days...\.\.\. my thoughts are so messed up,\. everything is confused in my head."

"One can only take sleep deprivation for so long until it starts to actually have some more serious effects...\.\.\. I have to figure this out before it gets to me or before I go crazy trying to find out!"
"This downward spiral into research is sending me straight down the abyss."
"A leaked report claims that experiments with stress induction are being performed in the Third Stratum and below."

"Animals are awakening to violent predatory instincts i the conditions they're placed in.\.\. Even docile,\. domesticated animals are lashing out against their peers and mauling them to near-death.\.\. Upon extended experimentation,\. many develop cannibalistic tendencies after being starved,\. forced to eat their own to survive."
"All this links back to someone whose name I've heard many times...\.\.\. "Head Researcher Moria"."
"Every time I start thinking about these things...\.\.\. my head feels like it's going to explode."

"Miss Kanako is barely letting me rest.\.\. I can't negotiate anything for getting night shifts because the schedule is already booked.\.\. Last time we spoke she told me I looked and talked like a maniac.\.\. The other maids are starting to avoid me too...\.\.\. am I actually going crazy?"

"The results \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Fifth Stratum\fn<GameFont>\fs[30] experiment about the \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Source were\fn<GameFont>\fs[30] completely wiped clean from the record,\. everything redacted!"
"\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Nothing\fn<GameFont>\fs[30] is true,\. noone can be trusted!"
"I have \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>proofs they are coming for me\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]!\.\. They know I know!"
"I'm \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>not safe here\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]!\.\. I have to protect myself!\.\. I can't let them get me!"
